#### text ####
text: That evening we saw some fascinating bioluminescence! (it was too faint to show up on camera). It made a long glowing line from the anchor all along one side of the ship and out the way past the back of the ship. It wasn't coming from anything solid and it would reform if we broke it. We'd never seen anything like it before! I also enjoyed watching the flashes of light from the fish darting around underwater. Bioluminescence is one of the most magical things about boating.
#### text ####
text: The next day, we got up early and had a fancy breakfast
